---
title: Speedy Chimichurri Chicken Rice Bowls with Chicken Thighs, Blistered Tomatoes & Zucchini
description: Traditional South American flavors transform classic chicken-and-veggies to delicious heights. You’ll sauté hearty chicken thighs with zucchini, red onion, and tomatoes, then toss with our garlicky, herbaceous chimichurri sauce and serve over fluffy steamed rice. The best part? It goes from box to table in a super-speedy 20 minutes!
